Lifecycle is ALWAYS same:
Trigger → Event → Lambda → Action → Response

Only TRIGGER changes:
├── API Gateway  → HTTP request from user
├── S3           → file uploaded
├── EventBridge  → scheduled time
├── Manual test  → you click test button
└── SNS/SQS      → message arrives

lambda_handler always receives event
Your code always runs same way
