With API Gateway trigger:

You hit URL:
POST https://api.example.com/ec2
Body: {"action": "start"}
        │
        ▼
API Gateway receives
        │
        ▼
Converts to Lambda event:
{
  "httpMethod": "POST",
  "body": "{\"action\": \"start\"}"
}
        │
        ▼
Lambda wakes up
        │
        ▼
Reads event.get('action') → "start"
        │
        ▼
ec2.start_instances()
        │
        ▼
Returns response
        │
        ▼
API Gateway sends back to you
